headline: Design Hotels Boosts Growth in Asia Pacific with Fourteen Landmark Signings
summary: Design Hotels, a global community for independent, design-driven hotels, has announced the addition of more than 14 properties across Asia Pacific, with the region accounting for a record 28% of the brand's overall portfolio global growth in 2025, a first for the brand.

headline: NagaCorp Featured Among Best in Region on Fortune 100 Best Companies to Work For™ Southeast Asia 2025 List
summary: NagaCorp Ltd. ("NagaCorp" or the "Company", SEHK Stock Code: 3918), a leading Integrated Resort operator in the Mekong Region, today announced its prestigious inclusion on the inaugural Fortune 100 Best Companies to Work For™ Southeast Asia list. Ranked number 46, NagaCorp stands as a leading Cambodian company on this prestigious roster, which recognises exemplary workplace cultures across the region.
